General.Name: Chordate Medical Holding AB
General.Description: Chordate Medical Holding AB (publ), a medical technology company, develops products and solutions for the treatment of chronic migraine and rhinitis in Sweden. It focuses on the ear-nose and throat area. Chordate Medical Holding AB (publ) was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Kista, Sweden.
